{"tid":497502,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"神魔之塔創辦人　6660萬入市天賦海灣","createTime":"2017-12-13T00:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T14:42:40.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c2f7859d6fab851873ace456f52e916a63402796","tid":497502,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T00:00:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1965000/1968300/pckn20130722003_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1965000%2F1968300%2Fpckn20130722003_600.jpg&h=9ecaa7f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據EPRC經濟地產庫資料顯示，天賦海灣3座7樓A及B室，其中A室面積1,704平方呎，B室則為1,715平方呎，兩個單位劃一作價3,330萬元，連車位以合共6,660萬元易手，實用呎價約2萬元。<br />\n<br />\n新買家分別是曾建中及曾建豪，兩人為手機程式開發商Madhead創辦人，近年推出熱門遊戲神魔之塔成名，該公司在2014年的估值一度達26億元，目前辦公室位於大埔科學園，比鄰天賦海灣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ps.hket.com/article/1968300/%E7%A5%9E%E9%AD%94%E4%B9%8B%E5%A1%94%E5%89%B5%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%BA%206660%E8%90%AC%E5%85%A5%E5%B8%82%E5%A4%A9%E8%B3%A6%E6%B5%B7%E7%81%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1968300%2F%25E7%25A5%259E%25E9%25AD%2594%25E4%25B9%258B%25E5%25A1%2594%25E5%2589%25B5%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25206660%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E8%25B3%25A6%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E7%2581%25A3&d=DGK2LAqmCD1msRExv7znd0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=a3de3543\" target=\"_blank\">http://ps.hket.com/article/1968300/%E7%A5%9E%E9%AD%94%E4%B9%8B%E5%A1%94%E5%89%B5%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%BA%206660%E8%90%AC%E5%85%A5%E5%B8%82%E5%A4%A9%E8%B3%A6%E6%B5%B7%E7%81%A3</a>"},{"pid":"b829f5a0e78c6d902b1c08437cb7183b6e11e8af","tid":497502,"uid":3764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T00:03:33.000Z","msg":"抄game都算抄得成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食正當時班仆街唔想睇日本"},{"pid":"bdbc0cc6dec8e03d7eda8e24906a9e64e99c7686","tid":497502,"uid":3764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"